    "This dataset, unfortunately, couldn't be expanded due to resource limitations.",
    "It's important to note that the data doesn't involve any human experimentation or usage of human tissue samples.",
    "Instead, it utilizes de-identified wound images, available at link: https:// github.",
    "com/ uwm-bigda ta/ Multi-modal-wound-class ifica tion-using-images-and-locat ions.",
    "Each image only includes the wound and immediate skin area, eliminating any unnecessary or personal data to protect patient identity."
